---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/article.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="AMS Eval - Support — jtdub.com" description="Get help with the AMS Eval app. Find answers to common questions, report issues, and request features.">
  <article class="article">
    <div class="article__body">
            <h1>AMS Eval &mdash; Support</h1>
            <p>Monitor Acute Mountain Sickness using the Lake Louise Score system. Designed for field use at high altitude.</p>

            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            <p>This app is currently in development. FAQs will be added as features are finalized.</p>

            <h2>Get Help</h2>

            <div>
                <h5>Report a Bug</h5>
                <p>Found something that isn't working right? Open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/jtdub/ams-eval-app/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">feedback repository</a> with a description of the problem.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h5>Request a Feature</h5>
                <p>Have an idea for improving AMS Eval? Submit a feature request on <a href="https://github.com/jtdub/ams-eval-app/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h5>Contact the Developer</h5>
                <p>For general questions or support inquiries, visit the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <hr>
            <p><a href="/apps/">&#8592; Back to Apps</a></p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
